{"tid":1773115,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"ony 香港公佈，會在 12 月中旬為 Xperia 1 及 Xperia 5 提供Android 10系統更新","createTime":"2019-12-07T08:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T03:02:55.000Z","uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85900a46c96f762c2df6162cd4720f035e866ed4","tid":1773115,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"Sony 香港公佈，會在 12 月中旬為 Xperia 1 及 Xperia 5 提供Android 10系統更新，手機升級後可配合 Google Assistant 享用更快捷的相機功能，透過語音指令啟動前置或後置相機進行拍攝及錄影。<br />\n升級後的新功能包括：<br />\n．Cinema Pro 加入「水平及水平校準」功能，在拍攝影片時可保持準確的水平範圍，另外 Xperia 1 更新後會同時獲得 Xperia 5 時加入的 Cinema Pro 新功能及遊戲增強器。<br />\n <br />\n．Android 10 支援更高彈性的分割屏幕比例，配合 21:9 CinemaWide 極闊屏幕可更方便地使用兩個程式，同時讀取不同資訊。<br />\n <br />\n．為STAMINA省電模式加入全新的深色主題背景 (dark mode)，當手機啟動該模式時，便會自動轉換深色主題背景，為用戶提供既省電又舒適的視覺體驗。<br />\n  <br />\nSony 亦將會為Xperia手機系列包括Xperia XZ2、XZ2C、XZ2P及XZ3提供Android 10系統更新，推出日期將於稍後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n快撚到'<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42c738d504e62af258981e3dc129ca50b8d5cb3","tid":1773115,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F